title: [Nielira Harbor, Cliffside]
description: An arch-inset limestone wall stands before the aerial view of the harbor below, the pillars framing the partition and hung with lattice-woven flora entwined with filament-like faenor vines.  Set upon a pedestal of starburst-inset marble is a bronze-banded telescope, the oiled instrument set before a half-circle of ebonwood benches nestled between patches of wildflowers.  Rows of topiaries flank the slate steps ascending the walkway, highlighting the lantern-draped iron gates set above the square.
